{{Han etyl}}
{{liushu|p}}: a woman ({{zh-l|*女}}) with two hands pointing to her midsection.

Original meaning was “waist” (now {{och-l|腰}}). The hands gradually shifted upwards; the {{zh-l|*覀}} in the modern form evolved from the hands and the woman's head.

{{zh-hanzi}}

# {{†}} to [[demand]]; to [[ask]]; to [[request]]
#: {{zh-x|要{yāo}求|to request}}
# {{†}} to [[force]]; to [[coerce]]
#: {{zh-x|要{yāo}脅|to threaten, to blackmail}}
# {{†}} to [[promise]]
#: {{zh-x|要{yāo}約|to restrict, to agree to a contract/offer/bid}}
# {{†}} to [[block]]; to [[intercept]]
#: {{zh-x|要{yāo}擊|to intercept, to ambush}}
# {{†}} {{zh-alt-form|邀|tr=-|to invite}}
# {{†}} {{zh-alt-form|腰|tr=-|waist}}
# {{†}} [[contract]] of [[alliance]]
#: {{zh-x|久要{yāo}|former '''contract'''}}
# {{surname|lang=zh}}
# to [[want]]

{{zh-hanzi}}

# to [[want]]; to [[wish]]; to [[need]]: to [[demand]]
#: {{zh-x|我 要 睡覺{jiào}。|I '''want''' to sleep.}}
#* {{zh-x|你 要 不 要 喝 茶？|Do you '''want''' some tea?}}
#* {{zh-x|老闆{bǎn} 要 我 馬上 回復。|My boss demanded that I reply immediately.}}
# [[will]]; [[going to]] {{qualifier|future auxiliary}}
#: {{zh-x|我 要 走 了。|I am '''going to''' go.}}
#* {{zh-x|我 怕 我們 要 遲到 了。|I fear that we '''will''' be late.}}
# [[about to]]
#* {{zh-x|出便 咁 黑，又 好似 要 落雨 噉。|It looks like it's going to rain outside.|C}}
# [[should]]; to [[must]]; to [[have to]]
#: {{zh-x|不要 喝 酒。|'''Don't''' drink alcohol.}}
#* {{zh-x|你 今天 一定 要 去 看病。|You '''must''' go to the doctor today.}}
#* {{zh-x|你 要 等 一會兒{r}，我 的 老闆[板] 現在 正 忙 得{de} 不可開交 。|You '''have to''' wait a moment. My boss is extremely busy now.}}
# [[vital]]; [[important]]
#: {{zh-x|重要|important}}
#: {{zh-x|主要|main}}
# [[if]]; [[in case]] of
#* {{zh-x|要 繫{jì} 腰帶，就 用不著[着]{zháo} 吊帶 了。|You don't need braces '''if''' you're wearing a belt.}}

